arts.ttl: Al-Hilal tops group with thrilling win over Nasaf Qarshi in Asian Champions League
arts.sum: Saudi Arabia’s Al-Hilal won at Uzbekistan’s Nasaf Qarshi 3-2 to move to the top of its group in the Asian Champions League Elite on Monday with maximum points from two games. “We should have won the game earlier however as we wasted many chances but Nasaf is a strong opponent.”

arts.ttl: Al Hilal 3-2 Nasaf Qarshi (29 de Sep., 2025) Resultado Final
